snippet.title: Depp vs. Heard, Britney Spears, & Other Celeb Cases: I Chat with Paralegal Debi Dooms (Part 1)
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp / Amber Heard / Britney Spears / Legal Analysis / Celeb Controversies / 

I chat with paralegal Debi Dooms and get her analysis about a number of controversial celeb cases, including Amber Heard & Johnny Depp, Britney Spears, etc. This is part 1 of a 2-part series. Part 2 will air on Debi's channel tomorrow, so subscribe to her channel for more. 

Part 2 will air on Debi's channel  tomorrow at this link: https://www.youtube.com/c/debidooms
